#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wallet subsystem provides a convenient and secure way to manage all your "
"passwords."
msgstr ""
"Podsistem novčanika pruža udoban i bezbedan način upravljanja svim vašim "
"lozinkama."

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"
msgstr "<keyword>KDE</keyword>"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Kwallet"
msgstr "K‑novčanik"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "passwords"
msgstr "lozinke"

#. Tag: keyword
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "forms"
msgstr "formulari"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Computer users have a very large amount of data to manage, some of which is "
"sensitive. In particular, you will typically have many passwords to manage. "
"Remembering them is difficult and writing them down on paper or in a text "
"file is insecure."
msgstr ""
"Korisnici računara često upravljaju velikom količinom podataka, od kojih su "
"neki poverljivi. U ovakve posebno spadaju lozinke. Pamtiti lozinke je teško, "
"a zapisivati ih na papir ili u tekstualni fajl nebezbedno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; provides a secure way to store passwords and other secret "
"information, allowing the user to remember only a single password instead of "
"numerous different passwords and credentials."
msgstr ""
"K‑novčanik 5 pruža bezbedan način za skladištenje lozinki i drugih tajnih "
"podataka, tako da korisnik treba da pamti samo jednu lozinku umesto brojnih "
"različitih lozinki i kredencijala."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a Wallet"
msgstr "Zatvaranje novčanika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallet is a password storage. It is usually sufficient to have just one "
"wallet secured by one master password but you can organize your large "
"collection of passwords by wallets using &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"Novčanik je skladište lozinki. Obično je dovoljno imati samo jedan novčanik "
"obezbeđen glavnom lozinkom, ali vam Menadžer K‑novčanika 5 omogućava i da "
"organizujete veliku zbirku lozinki u više novčanika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default a wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be used to "
"store your passwords. This wallet is secured by your login password and will "
"automatically be opened at login, if kwallet_pam is installed and properly "
"configured. On certain distros (&eg; Archlinux) kwallet_pam is not installed "
"by default"
msgstr ""
"Za skladištenje lozinki podrazumevano se koristi novčanik po imenu "
"<literal>kdewallet</literal>. Ovaj novčanik je obezbeđen vašom prijavnom "
"lozinkom, i biće automatski otvoren po prijavi, ako je <literal>kwallet_pam</"
"literal> instaliran i pravilno podešen. U pojedinim distribucijama (npr. "
"Arch Linux) <literal>kwallet_pam</literal> nije podrazumevano instaliran."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other wallets have to be opened manually."
msgstr "Ostali novčanici moraju ručno da se otvore."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are two ways to create a new wallet:"
msgstr "Nov novčanik može da se napravi na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the menu item <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>New "
"Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in the &kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr ""
"preko stavke menija <menuchoice><guimenu>Fajl</guimenu><guimenuitem>Novi "
"novčanik</guimenuitem></menuchoice> u Menadžeru K‑novčanika 5;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>New</guibutton> button in the &systemsettings; module "
"<guilabel>KDE Wallet</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"u Sistemskim postavkama, pomoću dugmeta <guibutton>Novi...</guibutton> u "
"modulu <guilabel>K‑novčanik</guilabel>;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have not created a wallet yet, see section <link linkend=\"kwallet-"
"using\">Using &kwallet5;</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ako još niste napravili novčanik, pogledajte odeljak <link linkend=\"kwallet-"
"using\">o korišćenju K‑novčanika 5</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; offers two different ways to store your data:"
msgstr "K‑novčanik 5 može da skladišti podatke na dva načina:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select encryption</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbor šifrovanja.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select encryption</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbor šifrovanja.</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blowfish encryption"
msgstr "šifrovanje Blowfishom"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; saves this sensitive data for you in a strongly encrypted file, "
"accessible by all applications, and protected with a master password that "
"you define."
msgstr ""
"K‑novčanik 5 upisuje osetljive podatke u snažno šifrovan fajl, dostupan svim "
"programima, a zaštićen glavnom lozinkom koju zadate."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Stvaranje novčanika šifrovanog Blowfishom.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Create a blowfish encrypted wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Stvaranje novčanika šifrovanog Blowfishom.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The data is encrypted with the <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish."
"html\">Blowfish symmetric block cipher algorithm</ulink>, the algorithm key "
"is derived from the <ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA-1 "
"hash</ulink> of the password, with a key length of 156 bits (20 bytes). The "
"data into the wallet file is also hashed with SHA-1 and checked before the "
"data is deciphered and accessible by the applications."
msgstr ""
"Podaci se šifruju <ulink url=\"http://www.schneier.com/blowfish.html"
"\">simetričnim blok‑šifrarskim algoritmom Blowfish</ulink>. Ključ algoritma "
"izvodi se iz <ulink url=\"http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc3174.txt\">SHA‑1 "
"disperzije</ulink> lozinke, i dužine je 156 bitova (20 bajtova). Podaci u "
"novčaniku takođe se disperziraju preko SHA‑1 i proveravaju pre nego što se "
"dešifruju i proslede programu."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid "GPG encryption"
msgstr "šifrovanje GPG‑om"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"GnuPG offers some very strong encryption algorithms and uses passphrase "
"protected long keys."
msgstr ""
"GnuPG poseduje neke vrlo snažne šifrarske algoritme, i koristi lozinke za "
"zaštitu dugačkih ključeva."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>No GPG key found</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Nema nijednog GPG ključa.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:132
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>No GPG key found</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Nema nijednog GPG ključa.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The screenshots above show the case where an encryption capable GPG key was "
"not found on the system. Please use applications like &kgpg; or &kleopatra; "
"to create a key and try again."
msgstr ""
"Gornji snimci ekrana pokazuju slučaj gde GPG ključ sposoban za šifrovanje "
"nije nađen na sistemu. Upotrebite program poput <application>KGPG‑a</"
"application> ili <application>Kleopatre</application> da napravite ključ, pa "
"pokušajte ponovo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a GPG key was found you will get the next dialog where you can select a "
"key to use for your new wallet."
msgstr ""
"Kada je GPG ključ nađen, dobićete naredni dijalog, u kome možete izabrati "
"ključ za potrebe novog novčanika."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select an encryption key</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Izbor šifrarskog ključa.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:144
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select an encryption key</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Izbor šifrarskog ključa.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; will now use GPG when storing wallets and when opening them. The "
"passphrase dialog only shows once. Even if the wallet is closed after "
"initial open, subsequent opening will occur silently during the same session."
msgstr ""
"Posle ovoga, K‑novčanik 5 će koristiti GPG pri skladištenju novčanikâ̂ i "
"čitanju iz njih. Dijalog za lozinku pojavljuje se samo jednom. Kada se "
"novčanik zatvori posle prvog otvaranja, naredna otvaranja unutar iste sesije "
"odigraće se nečujno."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same session can handle simultaneously both file formats. &kwallet5; "
"will transparently detect the file format and load the correct backend to "
"handle it."
msgstr ""
"Unutar jedne sesije, mogu se koristiti oba formata fajla. K‑novčanik 5 će "
"prozirno otkriti format fajla i učitati odgovarajuću pozadinu za njegovu "
"obradu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use your sensitive data from your classic wallet with the new backend "
"follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za korišćenje osetljivih podataka iz klasičnog formata novčanika sa novom "
"pozadinom, ispratite ove korake:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new GPG based wallet"
msgstr "Napravite novi novčanik na osnovi GPG‑a"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launch &kwalletmanager5; using &krunner; (<keycombo>&Alt; <keycap>F2</"
"keycap></keycombo>) or other application launcher (menu) and select your old "
"wallet. Then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Export "
"as encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> to create an archive file with your "
"sensitive data."
msgstr ""
"Pokrenite Menadžer K‑novčanika 5, preko <application>K‑izvođača</"
"application> (<keycombo><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>) "
"ili drugog pokretača programa (menija), i izaberite stari novčanik. Zatim "
"idite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Fajl</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izvezi šifrovano</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> da napravite fajl arhive sa osetljivim podacima."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the new GPG based wallet then choose <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select "
"the file you just saved."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite novi novčanik na osnovi GPG‑a, a zatim <menuchoice><guimenu>Fajl</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvezi šifrovano</guimenuitem></menuchoice> da "
"izaberete fajl koji ste upravo sačuvali."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to &systemsettings; <menuchoice><guimenu>Account Details</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>KDE Wallet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select the newly "
"created GPG based wallet from the <guilabel>Select wallet to use as default</"
"guilabel> combobox."
msgstr ""
"Idite u Sistemskim postavkama, <menuchoice><guimenu>Detalji naloga</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>K‑novčanik</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, pa izaberite "
"novostvoreni novčanik na osnovi GPG‑a iz liste <guilabel>Izaberite novčanik "
"će se podrazumevano koristiti:</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively use <guimenuitem>Import a wallet</guimenuitem> but in that "
"case you have to select the <filename class=\"extension\">.kwl</filename> "
"file corresponding to your old wallet, located in the folder <filename class="
"\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> in <userinput>qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno upotrebite <guimenuitem>Uvezi novčanik...</guimenuitem>, ali "
"tada morate da izaberete <filename class=\"extension\">.kwl</filename> fajl "
"koji odgovara starom novčaniku, a nalazi se u fascikli <filename class="
"\"directory\">kwalletd</filename> u <userinput>qtpaths --paths "
"GenericDataLocation</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; supports multiple wallets, so for the most secure operation, you "
"should use one wallet for local passwords, and another for network passwords "
"and form data. You can configure this behavior in the &kwallet5; "
"&systemsettings; module, however the default setting is to store everything "
"in one wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"K‑novčanik 5 podržava višestruke novčanike, te bi radi najveće bezbednosti "
"trebalo da koristite jedan novčanik za lokalne lozinke, a drugi za mrežne "
"lozinke i podatke formularâ̂. Ovo ponašanje možete podesiti u modulu "
"K‑novčanika 5 u Sistemskim postavkama. Podrazumevana postavka je ipak "
"skladištenje svega u jednom novčaniku po imenu <literal>kdewallet</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A wallet is by default closed, which means that you must supply a password "
"to open it. Once the wallet is opened, the contents can be read by any user "
"process, so this may be a security issue."
msgstr ""
"Novčanik je podrazumevano zatvoren, što znači da morate zadati lozinku da ga "
"otvorite. Pošto se otvori, njegovom sadržaju može pristupiti bilo koji "
"korisnički proces, što može biti bezbednosni problem."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Korišćenje K‑novčanika 5"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you visit &eg; the &kde; bugtracker and enter the login data for the "
"first time, a dialog pops up offering to store the password in an encrypted "
"wallet:"
msgstr ""
"Ako posetite npr. KDE‑ov pratilac grešaka i po prvi put unesete prijavne "
"podatke, iskočiće dijalog koji vam nudi da skladišti lozinku u šifrovani "
"novčanik:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to save login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zahtev za upisivanje prijavnih podataka.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to save login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zahtev za upisivanje prijavnih podataka.</phrase>"

# >! ui: Store --> ?
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to store this information, select <guibutton>Store</guibutton> "
"to proceed. In case you did not create a wallet so far, the next dialog asks "
"for the encryption backend and creates a wallet named kdewallet."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da skladištite ove podatke, kliknite na <guibutton>Skladišti</"
"guibutton> da nastavite. Ako još uvek niste napravili novčanik, sledeći "
"dijalog vam traži pozadinu za šifrovanje i stvara novčanik po imenu "
"<literal>kdewallet</literal>."

# rewrite-msgid: /with these secrets//
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next time you visit the same website again, the application retrieves the "
"login data from an open wallet and prefills the forms with these secrets."
msgstr ""
"Sledeći put kada posetite isti veb sajt, program dobavlja prijavne podatke "
"iz otvorenog novčanika i upisuje ih u formulare."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Prefilled login information</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Automatski ispunjeni prijavni podaci.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Prefilled login information</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Automatski ispunjeni prijavni podaci.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the wallet is closed the application requests to open the wallet. Enter "
"the wallet password and click the <guibutton>Open</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ako je novčanik zatvoren, program će zatražiti da ga otvori. Unesite lozinku "
"za novčanik i kliknite na dugme <guibutton>Otvori</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Zahtev za otvaranje novčanika.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Zahtev za otvaranje novčanika.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This connects the application to the wallet, enables it to read the login "
"data from the wallet and to restore the login information for this website. "
"Once an application is connected to the wallet, it can automatically restore "
"any login information stored in the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Ovo povezuje program s novčanikom, omogućavajući mu da pročita prijavne "
"podatke iz novčanika i pošalje ih veb sajtu. Pošto se program povezao s "
"novčanikom, može automatski pročitati sve prijavne podatke iz njega."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:251
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwalletmanager5;"
msgstr "Menadžer K‑novčanika 5"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwalletmanager5; serves a number of functions. Firstly it allows you to see "
"if any wallets are open, which wallets those are, and which applications are "
"using each wallet. You can disconnect an application's access to a wallet "
"from within the &kwalletmanager5;."
msgstr ""
"Menadžer K‑novčanika 5 ima brojne funkcije. Pre svega, omogućava vam da "
"vidite da li su neki novčanici otvoreni, koji su to novčanici i koji "
"programi ih koriste. Kroz Menadžer K‑novčanika možete otkazati pristup "
"programa novčaniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also manage the wallets installed on the system, creating and "
"deleting wallets and manipulating their contents (changing keys, ...)."
msgstr ""
"Možete i upravljati instaliranim novčanicima na sistemu, stvarati i brisati "
"novčanike, i manipulisati njihovim sadržajem (menjati ključeve, itd.)"

# rewrite-msgid: /application//
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kwalletmanager5; application is launched with <menuchoice> "
"<guimenu>Applications</guimenu><guisubmenu>System</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Wallet Management Tool</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the "
"application launcher. Alternatively start &krunner; with shortcut <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo> and enter "
"<command>kwalletmanager5</command>."
msgstr ""
"Menadžer K‑novčanika 5 se pokreće preko <menuchoice> <guimenu>Programi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Sistem</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Alatka za upravljanje "
"novčanicima</guimenuitem></menuchoice> u pokretaču programâ̂. Drugačije, "
"pokrenite <application>K‑izvođač</application> prečicom <keycombo action="
"\"simul\"><keycap>Alt</keycap><keycap>F2</keycap></keycombo>, pa unesite "
"<command>kwalletmanager5</command>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click once on the system tray wallet icon to display the &kwalletmanager5; "
"window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite jednom na ikonicu novčanika u sistemskoj kaseti da pozovete prozor "
"Menadžera K‑novčanika 5."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:273
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with one wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni prozor sa jednim novčanikom.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with one wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni prozor sa jednim novčanikom.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with one wallet</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavni prozor sa jednim novčanikom.</para>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Wallet Window"
msgstr "Prozor novčanika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have more than one wallet all available wallets are shown on the left."
msgstr ""
"Ako imate više od jednog novčanika, svi dostupni novčanici nabrojani su levo."

# >! "Form Data" and "Passwords" not translated in kdelibs/kdeui/util/kwallet.cpp.
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on a wallet in the &kwalletmanager5; window will display that "
"wallet's status and the contents of an opened wallet. A wallet may contain "
"any number of folders, which allow storing of password information. By "
"default a wallet will contain folders named Form Data and Passwords."
msgstr ""
"Klik na novčanik u prozoru Menadžera K‑novčanika 5 prikazuje stanje tog "
"novčanika i, ako je otvoren, njegov sadržaj. Novčanik može sadržati više "
"fascikli, u kojima se čuvaju podaci o lozinkama. Novčanik će podrazumevano "
"imati fascikle po imenu <guilabel>Podaci formulara</guilabel> i "
"<guilabel>Lozinke</guilabel>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Main window with two wallets</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Glavni prozor sa dva novčanika.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Main window with two wallets</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Glavni prozor sa dva novčanika.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:311
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Main window with two wallets</para>"
msgstr "<para>Glavni prozor sa dva novčanika.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <guibutton>Open</guibutton> to display the content of a closed wallet. "
"You will be requested to enter the master password."
msgstr ""
"Upotrebite <guibutton>Otvori...</guibutton> da prikažete sadržaj zatvorenog "
"novčanika. Biće vam traženo da unesete glavnu lozinku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Contents tab"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Contents</guilabel> tab has three sections:"
msgstr "Jezičak <guilabel>Sadržaj</guilabel> ima tri dela:"

# skip-rule: t-line
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "A search line to filter the items of the current wallet"
msgstr "Polje pretrage za filtriranje stavki u tekućem novčaniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The tree view of the folders contained in the wallet. Click the <guiicon>&gt;"
"</guiicon> / <guiicon>v</guiicon> icons to expand or collapse the tree view."
msgstr ""
"Prikaz stabla fascikli sadržanih u novčaniku. Kliktanjem na ikonice "
"<guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> i <guiicon>-</guiicon> širite i sažimate prikaz "
"stabla."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The contents of the selected folder entry at the right side. By default the "
"password and value are hidden. To display and edit them enable "
"<guilabel>Show values</guilabel> or click the <guilabel>Show Contents</"
"guilabel> button."
msgstr ""
"Sadržaj fascikle izabrane na desnoj strani. Lozinka i vrednost podrazumevano "
"su skrivene. Da biste ih prikazali, popunite <guilabel>Prikaži vrednosti</"
"guilabel> ili kliknite na dugme <guilabel>Prikaži sadržaj</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Folders may be added or deleted via the context menu, and selecting a folder "
"will update the folder entry list and the summary display. Selecting a "
"folder entry will update the entry contents pane, and allow you to edit that "
"entry."
msgstr ""
"Fascikle se mogu dodavati i brisati kroz kontekstni meni, a izborom jedne od "
"njih ažurira se spisak unosa fascikle i prikaz sažetka. Izborom unosa u "
"fascikli ažurira se okno sadržaja unosa, tako da ga možete urediti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entries may also be created, renamed or deleted via the context menu for the "
"folder contents."
msgstr ""
"Unosi se takođe mogu stvoriti, obrisati i preimenovati preko kontekstnog "
"menija u sadržaju fascikle."

# rewrite-msgid: /flash memory device/storage device/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All folders and entries may be dragged and dropped into other wallets or "
"folders respectively. This allows a user to easily package up a new wallet "
"for transfer to another environment. For instance, a new wallet could be "
"created and copied onto a removable flash memory device. Important passwords "
"could be transferred there, so you have them available in other locations."
msgstr ""
"Fascikle i unosi se mogu prevlačiti u druge novčanike i fascikle. Ovako "
"korisnik može lako spakovati novi novčanik za prenos u drugo okruženje. Na "
"primer, novi novčanik bi se mogao stvoriti ili kopirati na uklonjivi "
"skladišni uređaj i važne lozinke preneti u njega, tako da vam budu dostupne "
"na drugim lokacijama."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "Import and Export"
msgstr "Uvoz i izvoz"

# rewrite-msgid: /device//
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to transfer your secrets to another device or computer use the "
"actions in the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. With <guimenuitem>Export as "
"encrypted</guimenuitem> wallets can be exported into an encrypted archive "
"file. Importing this archive file with <guimenuitem>Import encrypted</"
"guimenuitem> you have to provide the master password of the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Ako želite da prenesete svoje tajne na drugi računar, poslužite se radnjama "
"iz menija <guimenu>Fajl</guimenu>. Pomoću <guimenuitem>Izvezi šifrovano</"
"guimenuitem> novčanici se izvoze u šifrovani fajl arhive. Pri uvozu ovakvog "
"fajla arhive, preko <guimenuitem>Uvezi šifrovano</guimenuitem>, moraćete da "
"unesete glavnu lozinku novčanika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively a <filename class=\"extension\">.xml</filename> file can be "
"used for transferring a wallet. Keep in mind that all secrets are stored as "
"plain text in this file."
msgstr ""
"Alternativno, za prenos fajla može da se upotrebi <filename class=\"extension"
"\">.xml</filename> fajl. Imajte na umu da su u takvom fajlu sve tajne "
"skladištene kao obični tekst."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Entries Manually"
msgstr "Ručno dodavanje unosa"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the context menu with the &RMB; click on <guilabel>Maps</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Passwords</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> tree view. "
"Select <guimenuitem>New</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>New Folder</"
"guimenuitem> and choose a name for the new entry."
msgstr ""
"Otvorite kontekstni meni desnim klikom na <guilabel>mape</guilabel> ili "
"<guilabel>lozinke</guilabel> prikazu stabla fascikli. Izaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Novi...</guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Nova fascikla...</"
"guimenuitem> i unesite ime nove stavke."

# rewrite-msgid: /Form Data/Maps/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the folder contents pane select <guilabel>New Folder</guilabel> from the "
"context menu of <quote>Form Data</quote> or <quote>Passwords</quote>. For "
"passwords click the <guilabel>Show Contents</guilabel> button, enter the new "
"password. For Maps you have to add a <guilabel>Key</guilabel> and a "
"<guilabel>Value</guilabel>. Click the <guilabel>Save</guilabel> button to "
"store the new entries in the encrypted wallet file."
msgstr ""
"U oknu sadržaja fascikle, izaberite <guilabel>Nova fascikla...</guilabel> iz "
"kontekstnog menija nad <guilabel>mape</guilabel> ili <guilabel>lozinke</"
"guilabel>. Za lozinke, kliknite na dugme <guilabel>Prikaži sadržaj</"
"guilabel> da unesete novu. Za mape, treba da dodate ključ i vrednost. "
"Kliknite na dugme <guilabel>Sačuvaj</guilabel> da bi se novi unosi "
"uskladištili u šifrovanom fajlu novčanika."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:378
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Applications tab</title>"
msgstr "<title>Jezičak <guilabel>Programi</guilabel></title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:381
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Applications tab</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Jezičak <guilabel>Programi</guilabel>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:387
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Applications tab</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Jezičak <guilabel>Programi</guilabel>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Applications tab</para>"
msgstr "<para>Jezičak <guilabel>Programi</guilabel>.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first list shows all applications currently connected to the selected "
"wallet. Use the button at the right side of each entry to disconnect the "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Prvi spisak prikazuje sve programe trenutno povezane na izabrani novčanik. "
"Dugmetom desno od svakog programa možete prekinuti njegovu vezu sa "
"novčanikom."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:396
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the second list all applications are displayed which are authorized to "
"access the wallet. Use the button right of each entry in the list to revoke "
"the access."
msgstr ""
"Na drugom spisku dati su svi programi koji su ovlašćeni za pristup "
"novčaniku. Upotrebite dugme desno od programa da mu povučete ovlašćenje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &kwallet5;"
msgstr "Podešavanje K‑novčanika 5"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:409
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Preferences"
msgstr "Postavke novčanika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kwallet5; contains a small configuration panel with several options that "
"allow you to tune &kwallet5; to your personal preferences. The default "
"settings for &kwallet5; are sufficient for most users."
msgstr ""
"K‑novčanik 5 sadrži mali panel za podešavanje, s nekoliko opcija kojima "
"možete prilagoditi K‑novčanik ličnom ukusu. Najvećem broju korisnika "
"odgovaraće podrazumevane postavke."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check the box to enable or disable the &kde; wallet subsystem entirely. If "
"this box is unchecked, then &kwallet5; is entirely disabled and none of the "
"other options here have any effect, nor will &kwallet5; record any "
"information, or offer to fill in forms for you."
msgstr ""
"Ovom kućicom možete potpuno uključiti ili isključiti KDE‑ov podsistem "
"novčanika. Pražnjenjem kućice K‑novčanik 5 se potpuno isključuje. Tada "
"nijedna druga opcija više nema nikakvog efekta, K‑novčanik neće pamtiti "
"nikakve podatke, niti nuditi da popunjava formulare umesto vas."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:421
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Wallet"
msgstr "Zatvaranje novčanika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:423
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when unused for:"
msgstr "Zatvori ako se ne koristi:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the current wallet after a period of inactivity. If you check this "
"option, set the period in the box, default is 10 minutes. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Novčanik se zatvara posle perioda neaktivnosti. Ako uključite ovu opciju, "
"period zadajete u polju; podrazumevani je 10 minuta. Pošto se novčanik "
"zatvori, potrebna je lozinka da bi mu se ponovo pristupilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when screensaver starts"
msgstr "Zatvori kada se pokrene čuvar ekrana"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as the screen saver starts. When a wallet is "
"closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Novčanik se zatvara čim se pokrene čuvar ekrana. Pošto se novčanik zatvori, "
"potrebna je lozinka da bi mu se ponovo pristupilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close when last application stops using it"
msgstr "Zatvori pošto programi prestanu da ga koriste"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Close the wallet as soon as applications that use it have stopped. Note that "
"your wallets will only be closed when all the applications that use it have "
"stopped. When a wallet is closed, the password is needed to access it again."
msgstr ""
"Novčanik se zatvara čim se završi program koji ga koristi. Ako ga koristi "
"više programa, novčanik će biti zatvoren kada svi oni prestanu s radom. "
"Pošto se novčanik zatvori, potrebna je lozinka da bi mu se ponovo pristupilo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Wallet Selection"
msgstr "Automatsko biranje novčanika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:453
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select wallet to use as default:"
msgstr "Izaberite novčanik će se podrazumevano koristiti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select which wallet you want to use as default wallet. Please keep in mind "
"that only the wallet named <guilabel>kdewallet</guilabel> will be opened "
"automatically at login, if this wallet and your login password are identical."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite koji novčanik želite da koristite kao podrazumevani. Imajte u vidu "
"da se samo novčanik po imenu <literal>kdewallet</literal> otvara automatski "
"po prijavljivanju, ako su vam prijavna lozinka i lozinka novčanika iste."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "Different wallet for local passwords:"
msgstr "Odvojeni novčanik za lokalne lozinke:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:466
#, no-c-format
msgid "If checked, choose a different wallet for local passwords."
msgstr "Ako je uključeno, za lokalne lozinke se koristi zaseban novčanik."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Wallet Manager"
msgstr "Menadžer novčanika"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show manager in system tray"
msgstr "Prikaži menadžer u sistemskoj kaseti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable the wallet manager to have its icon in the system tray."
msgstr "Uključuje menadžer novčanika i njegovu ikonicu u sistemskoj kaseti."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide System tray icon when last wallet closes"
msgstr "Sakrij ikonicu sistemske kasete po zatvaranju poslednjeg novčanika"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:484
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When there is no wallet in use anymore, remove the wallet icon from the "
"system tray."
msgstr ""
"Kada se više ne koristi nijedan novčanik, nestaje ikonica u sistemskoj "
"kaseti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, there is a button labeled <guibutton>Launch Wallet Manager</"
"guibutton>, which does precisely that."
msgstr ""
"Najzad, tu je dugme <guibutton>Pokreni menadžer novčanika</guibutton> koje "
"radi upravo to."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:492
#, no-c-format
msgid "This button is only visible if &kwalletmanager5; is not running"
msgstr "Ovo dugme je vidljivo samo kada Menadžer K‑novčanika 5 nije u pogonu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Access Control</title>"
msgstr "<title>Upravljanje pristupom</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:498
#, no-c-format
msgid "There is only one option on this page:"
msgstr "Na ovoj stranici ima samo jedna opcija:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prompt when an application accesses a wallet"
msgstr "Pitaj kada program pristupi novčaniku"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid "Signal you when an application gains access to a wallet."
msgstr "Signalizira vam kada program dobije pristup novčaniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next there is a tree style view of the access controls for your wallets."
msgstr "Zatim, tu je prikaz kontrola pristupa novčanicima u obliku stabla."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access Control</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Upravljanje pristupom.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access Control</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Upravljanje pristupom.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click with the &LMB; on the <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> symbol beside a wallet "
"name to expand the tree. You will see the name of each application that has "
"asked for access to the wallet, and the policy you set for it. You cannot "
"edit policies here, or add them, but it is possible to delete an entry by "
"&RMB; clicking on it and choosing <guimenuitem>Delete</guimenuitem> from the "
"context menu that appears, or by simply selecting it and pressing the "
"<keysym>Del</keysym> key."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite levim na simbol <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> pored imena novčanika da "
"proširite stablo. Videćete imena svih programa koji su tražili pristup "
"novčaniku i smernicu koju ste za to postavili. Ovde ne možete uređivati "
"smernice niti ih dodavati, ali je moguće obrisati unos desnim klikom na "
"njega i izborom <guimenuitem>Obriši</guimenuitem> iz kontekstnog menija, ili "
"izborom unosa i pritiskom tastera <keycap>Delete</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:531
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An application that has been allowed access to a wallet is granted access to "
"all passwords stored inside."
msgstr ""
"Program kome se dozvoli pristup novčaniku dobija pristup svim lozinkama "
"skladištenim u njemu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you erroneously configured an application not to use the &kwallet5; "
"delete the policy for this application here."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste nenamerno podesili neki program da ne koristi K‑novčanik 5, ovde "
"možete obrisati tu smernicu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the next start of this application you can define a new policy for access "
"to the wallet."
msgstr ""
"Na sledećem pokretanju tog programa možete zadati novu smernicu za pristup "
"novčaniku."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Access request to open a wallet</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Pristupni zahtev za otvaranje novčanika.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Access request to open a wallet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Pristupni zahtev za otvaranje novčanika.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:549
#, no-c-format
msgid "An application requesting access to a wallet"
msgstr "Program traži pristup novčaniku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced Features"
msgstr "Napredne mogućnosti"

# rewrite-msgid: /file browser/file manager/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Wallets can be dragged from the &kwalletmanager5; window. This allows you to "
"drag the wallet to a file browser window, where you can choose to copy, "
"move, or link the wallet, as desired."
msgstr ""
"Novčanici se mogu prevlačiti iz prozora Menadžera K‑novčanika 5. Tako možete "
"da prevučete novčanik u prozor menadžera fajlova, pa izabrati da li ćete ga "
"kopirati, premestiti ili povezati, po želji."

# rewrite-msgid: /keychain/stick/
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You might use this to save a wallet to portable media, such as a USB "
"keychain, so that you can take your passwords with you to work or on a "
"vacation, and still have easy access to important sites."
msgstr ""
"Ovako možete i upisati novčanik na prenosivi medijum, poput USB štapića, "
"tako da možete lozinke poneti sa sobom na posao ili na odmor, kako biste i "
"dalje lako pristupali važnim sajtovima."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Credits and License"
msgstr "Zasluge i licenca"

# literal-segment: &copy;
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kwallet5; &copy; 2003 &George.Staikos;"
msgstr ""
"K‑novčanik 5: © 2003, <personname><firstname>Džordž</firstname> "
"<surname>Stajkos</surname></personname>."

